# Default Certificate Background Placeholder

This is a placeholder file for the default certificate background image.
Please replace this with an actual JPG image file.

The certificate background should be:
- 297mm x 210mm (A4 Landscape) at 300 DPI (3508 x 2480 pixels)
- JPG format
- Professional certificate design with:
  - Border or frame design
  - Subtle watermark or pattern
  - Space for certificate content in the center
  - Light colors that won't interfere with text

You can use services like:
- Canva (search for "certificate templates")
- Freepik (search for "certificate background")
- Or create your own certificate background design

Recommended design elements:
- Elegant border with ornamental corners
- Subtle gradient or texture
- Company logo watermark
- Gold/blue/professional color scheme